el_Goodfellow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10m synchro\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was with Lee that Daley would finally win that elusive gold medal, winning the same event in Tokyo in 2021.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.8069752791762456, \"rank\": 0.23872692180332794, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2246, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6824266295481861, \"rank\": 0.4653388185465815, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"that elusive gold medal\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"the same event\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley finally had the gold that many felt his career deserved and, by 2023, when he and husbandDustin Lance Blackwelcomed theirsecond sonand he had not competed for two years, his diving career seemed over.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"husbandDustin Lance\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"his diving career\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley evenwent as far as accepting punditry rolesahead of Paris 2024, but hereturned to British Swimming's World Class Programmein November of last year,after his son urged him to make a U-turnand target Olympic qualification.\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2527, \"end\": 2537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.384491165785642e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2557, \"end\": 2573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Swimming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley evenwent\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"punditry rolesahead\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2523}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"a U-turnand target Olympic qualification\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, having teamed up with Noah Williams ahead of the Games, Daley enters his fifth Olympics, having qualified in February after the pair won silver in the 10m synchro at the World Aquatics Championships.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2724, \"end\": 2737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"hi